snippet: LaRoche came off the bench in the ninth inning and drove in five runs to lead the Washington Nationals to a thrilling 8-5 victory over the host Los Angeles Dodgers on Wednesday.
abstract: Baseball Roundup; Washington Nationals first baseman Adam LaRoche comes off bench in ninth inning and drives in five runs to lead team to a 8-5 victory over Los Angeles Dodgers; other MLB scores noted.
lead_paragraph: LaRoche came off the bench in the ninth inning and drove in five runs to lead the Washington Nationals to a thrilling 8-5 victory over the host Los Angeles Dodgers on Wednesday.

headline.main: Adam LaRoche Has 5 R.B.I. Off the Bench to Lift the Nationals
